title: Raiders: Amari Cooper lets actions, others do the talking for him
text:
Photo: Joe Robbins, Getty Images Two-time Pro Bowl cornerback Joe Haden of the Browns could do little but watch as Raiders’ rookie wide receiver Amari Cooper pulled in eight catches for 134 yards in Oakland’s 27-20 Week 3 win. Two-time Pro Bowl cornerback Joe Haden of the Browns could do...
Luther Campbell wanted to make sure someone noticed the quiet kid, so he hit the field at Florida State talking.
